'''Wayne Pygram''' (born [[October 13]], [[1950s#1959|1959]]) is an [[Wikipedia:Australians|Australian]] actor who briefly portrayed a younger [[Wilhuff Tarkin]] at the end of the [[2005]] [[prequel trilogy]] film {{Film|III}}.<ref name="III" /> He was noted for his almost uncanny resemblance to original Tarkin actor [[Peter Cushing]]. He is mainly known for his dual role of [https://farscape.fandom.com/wiki/Scorpius Scorpius] and [https://farscape.fandom.com/wiki/Harvey Harvey] on the space opera TV show ''Farscape'' (1999-2004).

